snippet.title: Angry Birds Hatchery Island (Gameplay) | 12-17-23
snippet.description:
Original upload: https://x.com/angry_facts/status/1736480371154305485

https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1RXRhIHhouwxRflH5PBJNtzVG0TQMwqQC?usp=sharing

https://discord.gg/6QCeqKJWp3 (Hidden Birds Discord server)


—————————————————————

Fact #3095: As part of the recent mobile teraleak, an unreleased Angry Birds game was found, known as either “Angry Birds Hatchery” or “Angry Birds Island”.

The game as it was found includes a Hatchery mode, which is seemingly a customizable Island, alongside unique birds.
